员工还可以申请劳动仲裁吗？ 3. 若以上两点，若公司不算违法，也承认了员工，那员工被侵犯的权益该如何维护呢？难道真的要继续留下上班，然后待不下去了自己主动离职吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-c91557925b1b923f147e11ec5d079dc5_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/458446577"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I28es9omwiIsVEAMaCDY0MTU3NDI5INb52oQGMCw4xSBALnIJNDU4NDQ2NTc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1632801764.3045824", "card_id": "Q_487830615", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 158}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "出门旅游，有哪些东西即使你行李再多，也一定会带的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cdab0e65eb9dc4f0eec4dbd777de5c89.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/487830615"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I28es9omwiIsVEAMaCDcwNjg4NDUyINaunIoGMAE4mQJAL3IJNDg3ODMwNjE1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1632801764.304976", "card_id": "Q_489263490", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 196}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "国务院研究推动「将 3 岁以下婴幼儿照护服务费用纳入个人所得税专项附加扣除」，会带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "国务院印发中国妇女发展纲要和中国儿童发展纲要，要求完善人口生育相关法律法规政策，推动生育政策与经济社会政策配套衔接。研究推动将 3 岁以下婴幼儿照护服务费用纳入个人所得税专项附加扣除、住房等方面支持政策，减轻家庭生育、养育、教育负担。 来源：中国政府网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-19e1ba85f97facb18aa4c95825ef91ba_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/489263490"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I28es9omwiIsVEAMaCDcxMDA2NzEyIK3ZxIoGMBk4rwRAMHIJNDg5MjYzNDkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1632801764.3054726", "card_id": "Q_489